OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1783667970
OL,3,CMeghan will not join Harry in public
OL,4,Cbut may still come to the UK
OL,6,FIt has been confirmed that the Duchess
OL,7,Fof Sussex will not accompany her
OL,8,Fhusband Prince Harry on any of his UK
OL,9,Fvisits this week.
OL,11,FMeghan was scheduled to appear
OL,12,Falongside Harry at events including
OL,13,Fthe ceremony to mark a year to go
OL,14,Funtil the Invictus Games in Birmingham.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
