PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1783667970
OL,3,CMeghan will not join Harry in public
OL,4,Cbut may still come to the UK
OL,6,FBut after long discussions centred
OL,7,Faround the lack of state-funded
OL,8,Fsecurity for the Duke and Duchess of
OL,9,FSussex when they are in the UK, her
OL,10,Foffice has confirmed she will not be
OL,11,Fat any of the public events he is
OL,12,Fattending.
OL,14,FThe biggest event is Friday's Invictus
OL,15,FGames gathering at the NEC in
OL,16,FBirmingham, which is hosting the
OL,17,Ftournament for wounded, injured and
OL,18,Fsick military veterans in July 2027.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1783667970
OL,3,CMeghan will not join Harry in public
OL,4,Cbut may still come to the UK
OL,6,FThe couple's office had previously
OL,7,Fannounced the Duke and Duchess would
OL,8,Fbe attending together - along with
OL,9,Fsome of the other charity events Harry
OL,10,Fhad in his diary for this week.
OL,12,FBut when the committee which decides
OL,13,Fon Harry and Meghan's security
OL,14,Fprotection during their time in the UK
OL,15,Ftold the couple they would not get any
OL,16,Fstate-level protection, it was decided
OL,17,FHarry would attend the events alone.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
