OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1783667970
OL,3,CMeghan will not join Harry in public
OL,4,Cbut may still come to the UK
OL,6,FITV News understands last minute
OL,7,Fdiscussions have been taking place in
OL,8,Fthe last few days over a meeting
OL,9,Fbetween Prince Harry and his father,
OL,10,FKing Charles.
OL,12,FThey are trying to find a mutually
OL,13,Fconvenient time and location for the
OL,14,Ffather and son to see each other, but
OL,15,Fstaff in both camps are suspicious of
OL,16,Fthe others' motives.
OL,18,FThe latest arrangements centre on
OL,19,FHarry travelling 90 minutes from
OL,20,FBirmingham to meet the King at his
OL,21,FHighgrove estate in Glouchestershire.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1783667970
OL,3,CMeghan will not join Harry in public
OL,4,Cbut may still come to the UK
OL,6,FHarry is trying to work out a way for
OL,7,Fhis family to travel there too as he
OL,8,Fis keen for his two children, Prince
OL,9,FArchie and Princess Lilibet, to see
OL,10,Ftheir grandfather.
OL,12,FThe last time King Charles saw his two
OL,13,FCalifornia-based grandchildren was in
OL,14,Fthe summer of 2022 - meaning they have
OL,15,Fnever met him as King.
OL,17,FHowever, there is some briefing taking
OL,18,Fplace on both sides about the
OL,19,Fwillingness of the other side to meet
OL,20,F- or to find a time which works for
OL,21,Fthe King and Harry.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30506
