OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1783667970
OL,3,CMeghan will not join Harry in public
OL,4,Cbut may still come to the UK
OL,6,FHarry and Meghan plan to take Archie
OL,7,Fand Lilibet to see their paternal
OL,8,Fgrandmother's grave.
OL,10,FThe Spencer family reunion on Friday
OL,11,Fand Saturday will include all of
OL,12,FDiana's siblings, Charles Spencer,
OL,13,FLady Jane Fellowes and Lady Sarah
OL,14,FMcCorquodale.
OL,16,FIf King Charles is at his Highgrove
OL,17,Festate this weekend, it is unlikely
OL,18,FQueen Camilla will also be there after
OL,19,Fthe negative comments Harry made about
OL,20,Fher in his book, Spare.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
