OL,3,CMeghan will not join Harry in public
OL,4,Cbut may still come to the UK
OL,6,FThe Queen does have a private family
OL,7,Fhome in Wiltshire where she does often
OL,8,Fstay at weekends.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FIt has been a difficult week for
OL,16,FPrince Harry who was told he had left
OL,17,Fit too late to accept a room at
OL,18,FBuckingham Palace during his visit to
OL,19,FLondon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
