OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1783667970
OL,3,CMeghan will not join Harry in public
OL,4,Cbut may still come to the UK
OL,6,FAs fifth in line to the throne, and
OL,7,Fwith children who are sixth and
OL,8,Fseventh in line, Harry argues the
OL,9,Fthreats to the safety of his family is
OL,10,Fheightened in the UK, especially as he
OL,11,Ffought in Afghanistan for the British
OL,12,FArmy.
OL,14,FIn Birmingham on Friday, Harry will
OL,15,Fmeet many of the competitors who have
OL,16,Fsuffered injured or sickness during
OL,17,Ftheir time in the military.
OL,19,FThe Duke founded the Invictus Games in
OL,20,F2014 after his second tour of duty in
OL,21,FAfghanistan.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
