OL,3,CMeghan will not join Harry in public
OL,4,Cbut may still come to the UK
OL,6,FBirmingham is a location that means a
OL,7,Flot to many of the injured veterans,
OL,8,Fas many were flown back to the city's
OL,9,FQueen Elizabeth hospital from
OL,10,Ftreatment after suffering life-
OL,11,Fchanging injuries on the battlefield.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
